	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">王建华委员：</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">您提出的关于在环保压力下印刷关联产业创新转型路径的建议的提案收悉，经研究，现答复如下：</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、关于“环保部门应该积极与行业协会及行业专家一起制定行业环保要求下的转型路径及路线图”问题。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">依据江苏省委省政府的统一部署，昆山市人民政府于</SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2017" Month="3" Day="13" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>13</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">出台了《昆山市挥发性有机物污染治理专项行动实施方案》（昆政办发</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">〔</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">〕</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>45</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">号），要求全力推进重点工业行业</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">治理，完成包括印刷包装行业的主要</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">排放行业的综合治理，努力推进各行业转型升级。</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">印刷包装行业的</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">治理具体目标是：</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年底前，完成昆山正威印刷包装有限公司等印刷包装行业重点企业</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>26</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家（见附件）</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">综合治理。</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年底前，基本完成印刷包装行业综合治理。</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">综合治理的总体思路是：以源头控制、结构优化、综合治理、总量控制为原则，通过采用结构调整、原料替代、过程管理、排放监控、末端治理等全过程污染管控措施，全面开展</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">减排工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">印刷包装行业</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">减排的主要方式是：使用水性、大豆基、紫外光固化等低</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">含量的油墨替代溶剂型油墨，使用无溶剂、水性胶等环境友好型复合技术替代溶剂型胶水；对转运、储存等环节，采取密闭措施；加强有机废气分类收集与处理，收集的废气采取回收、焚烧等末端治理措施；加强管理，建立台账记录生产原料、辅料的使用量、废弃量、去向以及挥发性有机物含量；记录生产设备、废气收集</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>/</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">处理设备日常运行、维护、维修情况（台账保存三年）；定期委托第三方进行废气排放情况监测（依据废气处理设施每年</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1-4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">次不等），重点监控企业应按要求安装</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>VOCs</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">在线监测设施。</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、关于“政府要出台一定的资助政策，对企业用于环保设备、绿色工艺及数字设备的技改投入等，加大资金扶持力度，让企业在承担责任的同时也得到一定的政府资助”问题。</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1"> </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">市经信委今年出台了《昆山市关于推进转型升级创新发展（工业经济）财政扶持若干政策实施细则》（昆经信〔</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">〕</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>16 </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">号）文件，对于提案中提及的企业用于环保设备、绿色工艺与数字设备的技改项目，只要符合相关条件，均可以申报我市企业技术改造、节能环保等项目，验收通过后，可以享受相关资金扶持政策。</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">感谢您对我市产业发展的关注，希望在今后的工作中继续得到您的关心和支持。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 216pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 13.5" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">昆山市经济和信息化委员会</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </SPAN>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>12</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
